      "endLine": 487,
      "endCol": 2
    },
    {
      "text": "// PosFromByte computes a 1-based line/col Position for a byte offset in source.\n// It is the exported entry point used by the cache-sync reconstruction path to\n// derive chunk positions from stored byte offsets.\nfunc PosFromByte(source []byte, off int) Position {\n\treturn posFromByte(source, off)\n}",
      "contextualizedText": "// internal/chunk/code.go \u003e function PosFromByte\n\n// PosFromByte computes a 1-based line/col Position for a byte offset in source.\n// It is the exported entry point used by the cache-sync reconstruction path to\n// derive chunk positions from stored byte offsets.\nfunc PosFromByte(source []byte, off int) Position {\n\treturn posFromByte(source, off)\n}",
      "headingContext": "internal/chunk/code.go \u003e function PosFromByte",
      "startLine": 489,
      "startCol": 1,
      "endLine": 494,
      "endCol": 2
    },
    {
      "text": "// posFromByte computes a 1-based line/col Position for a byte offset in source.\nfunc posFromByte(source []byte, off int) Position {\n\tline, col := 1, 1\n\tfor i := 0; i \u003c off \u0026\u0026 i \u003c len(source); i++ {\n\t\tif source[i] == '\\n' {\n\t\t\tline++\n\t\t\tcol = 1\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tcol++\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\treturn Position{Line: line, Col: col}\n}",
      "contextualizedText": "// internal/chunk/code.go \u003e function posFromByte\n\n// posFromByte computes a 1-based line/col Position for a byte offset in source.\nfunc posFromByte(source []byte, off int) Position {\n\tline, col := 1, 1\n\tfor i := 0; i \u003c off \u0026\u0026 i \u003c len(source); i++ {\n\t\tif source[i] == '\\n' {\n\t\t\tline++\n\t\t\tcol = 1\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tcol++\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\treturn Position{Line: line, Col: col}\n}",
      "headingContext": "internal/chunk/code.go \u003e function posFromByte",
